                    <p>Because we are aware of the impact our furniture has on the planet, we make conscious decisions
                        in every aspect of our design process about how to minimise the environmental impact of our
                        furniture and extend its lifetime.</p>

                    <p>We craft each piece with care and use responsibly sourced materials such as sustainably certified
                        wood and recycled fabrics. Our furniture is customisable to suit the customers’ needs, and
                        made-to-order to avoid excess stock. Our entire collection is produced in Europe, a great deal
                        of it even in the Netherlands. To ensure our products never end up as waste, we offer various
